title: Nerding out LIVE in LA: Tolkien, Rings of Power, Mario Bros & Star Wars!
description:
I'm doing a special in-person stream alongside Cliff & Justin from  @TheOneRingNet  during their TORn Tuesday stream, live at Scum & Villainy Cantina in LA!

Topics include:
Tolkien (ofc!)
Rings of Power's 37% retention rate
Mario Bros Movie & its love of the source material
Star Wars - news from Celebration & the future

#lordoftherings #tolkien #starwars
